                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For the texts of a letter from Acting Secretary of Defense Robert A. Lovett to
                    Secretary Acheson, March 31, and an enclosed memorandum from the Joint Chiefs of
                    Staff to the Secretary of Defense, March 27, both of which concerned, in part,
                    the questions of Formosa and Chinese representation in the United Nations, see
                        <ref target="frus1951v07p1#pg_285">page 285</ref>.</p>
            </div>
